original_title: Reykjavik, des elfes dans la ville
overview: David, Tinna, Svanhvit, Hrönn and Oli live in Reykjavik, are less than 25 years old and work during summer while pursuing their studies during winter. In their eyes reflects the want to cross the sea and discover the world just like their ancestor Erik the Red.
title: Reykjavik, des elfes dans la ville
